                <pb facs="0340" n="320" xml:id="pg_320"/>
                <p rend="flushleft">1. <hi rend="italic">Records of Previous Meetings</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council approved the records of the 4th, 6th, 7th, 8th and 9th Meetings.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">2. <hi rend="italic">Report by the Deputies to the Council</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Mr. Vyshinski submitted a report by the Deputies on the progress of the
                    preparation of the draft treaties with Italy, Roumania, Bulgaria, Hungary and
                    Finland.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">3. <hi rend="italic">U.S. Delegation’s Proposal for the Meeting
                        of the Peace Conference</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">agreed</hi> to continue the discussion of this question
                    at the next meeting.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">4. <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting of the Council</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council <hi rend="italic">agreed</hi> to hold its next meeting at 11 a.m. on
                    10th May.</p>
